  ggplot(aes(x = Deaths,  y = reorder(Country_Region, Deaths))) + 
    geom_bar(stat = 'identity') +
    ggtitle("The 10 countries with the most reported COV19-related deaths") +
    ylab("Country/Region") +
    xlab("Deaths")
